OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774372288
OL,3,CAverage of 18 deaths a week linked to
OL,4,CA&E wait times, new data shows
OL,6,FNearly 1,000 deaths in Wales were
OL,7,Flinked to long A&E waiting times in
OL,8,F2025, latest data shows.
OL,10,FData from the Royal College of
OL,11,FEmergency Medicine (RCEM) estimates
OL,12,Fthat 965 deaths across the country
OL,13,Fwere associated with waits of 12 hours
OL,14,For more.
OL,16,FThat's an average of 18 people per
OL,17,Fweek and an increase of 29 deaths
OL,18,Fcompared to 2024.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
