OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774372288
OL,3,CAverage of 18 deaths a week linked to
OL,4,CA&E wait times, new data shows
OL,6,FDr. Rob Perry, RCEM Vice President for
OL,7,FWales, described the figures as a
OL,8,F"tragedy" that "should send shockwaves
OL,9,Fthrough the entire political system."
OL,11,FHe added: "My heart goes out to the
OL,12,Floved ones of any person who died
OL,13,Ffollowing long waits in emergency
OL,14,Fdepartments (EDs).
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774372288
OL,3,CAverage of 18 deaths a week linked to
OL,4,CA&E wait times, new data shows
OL,6,F"These may have been our most
OL,7,Fvulnerable patients, those deemed sick
OL,8,For injured enough to require
OL,9,Fadmission. They should be receiving
OL,10,Fthe best care promptly; instead, they
OL,11,Fare often the ones who wait the
OL,12,Flongest."
OL,14,FHe attributed the deaths to a
OL,15,F"breakdown in patient flow" and a
OL,16,Fcritical lack of hospital beds, and
OL,17,Fnoted that departments are frequently
OL,18,Fat capacity because of "exit block";
OL,19,Fthe difficulty of discharging patients
OL,20,Fthrough the hospital's "back door."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774372288
OL,3,CAverage of 18 deaths a week linked to
OL,4,CA&E wait times, new data shows
OL,6,F"Addressing this, rather than focusing
OL,7,Fon diverting people away from the
OL,8,F'front door' of EDs, is the best way
OL,9,Fto fix long waits," he added.
OL,11,FWith the Senedd elections approaching,
OL,12,Fthe RCEM is calling on all political
OL,13,Fparties to prioritise hospital
OL,14,Fcapacity to end overcrowding.
OL,16,FResponding to the findings, a Welsh
OL,17,FGovernment spokesperson said: "Too
OL,18,Fmany people are waiting too long in
OL,19,Femergency departments.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774372288
OL,3,CAverage of 18 deaths a week linked to
OL,4,CA&E wait times, new data shows
OL,6,F"Long stays are distressing for
OL,7,Fpatients and families and can be
OL,8,Fassociated with poorer outcomes,
OL,9,Fparticularly for older people or those
OL,10,Fwho have complex clinical needs.
OL,12,F"We have been clear that health boards
OL,13,Fmust improve flow, eliminate 12-hour
OL,14,Fstays and care in temporary spaces.
OL,16,F"We are working with the NHS,
OL,17,Fcouncils, and NHS Performance and
OL,18,FImprovement to reduce pressures by
OL,19,Fdeveloping safe community alternatives
OL,20,Fand extra social care capacity.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
